OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in his underwear
OL,6,FWATCH: The moment Kent Police officers
OL,7,Funcover bags of drugs hidden behind
OL,8,Fcar speakers.
OL,10,FA drug dealer who was found hiding
OL,11,Fnearly 60 bags of Class A substances
OL,12,Fin his underwear has been jailed.
OL,14,FPolice in Tunbridge Wells, Kent, also
OL,15,Ffound three containers full of
OL,16,Fcocaine, heroin, cash and a set of
OL,17,Fscales belonging to Ramesses Yebiemen,
OL,18,Fwhich were hidden in the speakers of a
OL,19,Fcar.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
