OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781179880
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in his underwear
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old was stopped last
OL,7,FFebruary by officers from the
OL,8,FNeighbourhood Task Force, who were
OL,9,Fpatrolling near Oak Road when they
OL,10,Fnoticed him acting suspiciously.
OL,12,FThey followed the vehicle, which was
OL,13,Fparked on Rymers Close, and detained
OL,14,FYebiemen.
OL,16,FDuring a search, he handed over 57
OL,17,Fwraps of Class A drugs, which were
OL,18,Fhidden in his underwear.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781179880
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in his underwear
OL,6,FOfficers then noticed the car speakers
OL,7,Fwere easy to remove and found the
OL,8,Fother containers.
OL,10,FYebiemen, of Higher Road in Haringey,
OL,11,FLondon, was arrested and later charged
OL,12,Fwith intent to supply Class A drugs,
OL,13,Fpossession of criminal property and
OL,14,Fdriving without insurance.
OL,16,FHe was sentenced at Maidstone Crown
OL,17,FCourt earlier this month to two years
OL,18,Fand four months in prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
