PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781179880
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in his underwear
OL,6,FKent Police Sergeant Ed Kavanagh said:
OL,7,F"Officers from our Neighbourhood Task
OL,8,FForce are always quick to spot
OL,9,Fsuspicious behaviour and will take
OL,10,Fprompt action to tackle those who come
OL,11,Fto their attention.
OL,13,F"In this case, they could tell
OL,14,FYebiemen was up to no good from the
OL,15,Fmanner of his driving.
OL,17,F"He was stopped and despite his
OL,18,Fefforts to hide his stash, multiple
OL,19,Fdeals of heroin and cocaine were
OL,20,Frecovered."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
