PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1781179880
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in his underwear
OL,6,FSgt Kavanagh added: "He is now
OL,7,Fstarting a prison sentence and I would
OL,8,Fwarn any other dealers who are
OL,9,Fconsidering travelling to Kent to
OL,10,Fthink again.
OL,12,F"You are likely to share the same fate
OL,13,Fas this criminal."
